{"tid":1579105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運動之後的方向(part 1) (長文慎入)","createTime":"2019-09-18T12:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T12:17:02.000Z","uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f27e349ad1c5def0d518f57d7e7a337bad28caf5","tid":1579105,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:13:26.000Z","msg":"尋晚的聽證會, 我相信大家都係好感動, 大家都見到曙光<br />\n(Btw我估唔到班美國議員仲激過我地, 我個刻好驚Mr. Smith 啲血壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n但係之後呢? <br />\n同埋美國&lt;香港人權及民主法案&gt; 始終變數太多, 你估中共會唔會咁順灘俾條例過? <br />\n1. 支那一定會出盡力去抹黑我地, 抹黑運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ne.g. 扮黃絲不停出fake news, 引誘成班連登仔女去(包括我)fc, 甚至令我地自己都spread 埋fake news 令我地在國際的公信力下降<br />\n(仲有好多我地想像唔到的)<br />\n2. 用錢,利益收買etc呢啲野, 呢啲招一定出唔少<br />\n<br />\n簡單來講, 未到正式通過個一刻, 文宣不能少, 即使有奶共議員, 都要令佢個州的巿民支持我地 (p.s. 929係一個好好的宣傳日子, 記得要宣傳#Chinazi<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 令佢不得不支持法案<br />\n<br />\n好, 回歸正題, 咁之後呢?<br />\n<br />\n小弟而家拋下磚, 希望有大大幫手諗下 (想法同方向only, 小弟無錢, 所以做唔到野)<br />\n分開左幾方面 (會分幾個post打出來, 有人有興趣先繼續打)<br />\n<br />\n1. 保持初心<br />\n我知道大家都會好惱, 特別係721, 831仲有最近的屍體發現。<br />\n(利申: 我係信當中有人被打死, 輪姦, 但以下說話, 係難聽, 不過都要講) <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">查到真相又如何?</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你會即時沖出去劏狗嗎?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記得當初我地出來係為了<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求(特別係真普選, 打倒殺人政權)</span></span>, 如果我地為左一時怒火, 令我地成個運動collapse, <span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地先真正對唔住烈士同個啲因此而犠牲的人命</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n所以, <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家要記得我地的初心, 即使憤怒, 都要忍住 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(p.s. 唔係唔俾你爆, 但要係岩的時侯, 先會事半功倍), <br />\n</span></span><br />\n以現況來講: <br />\n唔係唔查明真相, 而係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同步進行</span></span>, <br />\n一方面要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">繼續爭取雙普選</span></span>, 重建三權分立, esp司法獨立<br />\n另一方面, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盡量搵證據, 但要存起</span></span>(除非證據確鑿, 班popo無得抵賴, 連國際社會都會認同我地的行動), 等到司法獨立之日(審判日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"e9b1e441733ef8eebf126b286279e89e0347da6c","tid":1579105,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:13:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1dcd5e8cbea037cc8e037d081a073e60652f513e","tid":1579105,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7aeecb521f6c2c2cac7eb760837a35e9f71759bc","tid":1579105,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:14:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3cae931b2f4c13fd1bace8ad4e69025e84bf7a52","tid":1579105,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"706bf240f9af88f124ec00b73736b884c0666aef","tid":1579105,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:14:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"126107752c53ebb88b965f2b3cbb42eea9c13ade","tid":1579105,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:14:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6956cedf23cf60ce04e32cff7e470ca282183a6a","tid":1579105,"uid":261544,"like":0,"disl